name: Imposter (Lexingto, Yacob)
description:
Game Info:
Its mid fall, you're on a late night drive home in the dark and suddenly feel a thud under your car and take a turn for the worst. You come to, with your car written off and nothing but a simple flash light and a first aid kit! Find your way out of the forest before you discover what that thud under your car was!!!
